subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Sixth-seeded Juan Martín Del Potro stunned Roger Federer, 3-6, 7-6 (5), 4-6, 7-6 (4), 6-2, and claimed the men’s singles title, which Federer had won the past five years.
